                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "We serve Vancouver, Burnaby, Surrey, Richmond, Coquitlam, Langley, Delta, New Westminster, North Vancouver, West Vancouver, Maple Ridge, Pitt Meadows, Port Coquitlam, Port Moody, White Rock, Tsawwassen and Ladner."
              }
            },
            {
              "@type": "Question",
              "name": "Why do Metro Vancouver homes need regular exterior cleaning?",
              "acceptedAnswer": {
                "@type": "Answer",
                "text": "Frequent rain, tree debris, and moss growth can quickly lead to blocked gutters, slippery surfaces, stained siding, and roof wear. Routine cleaning helps protect the home and reduce repair risk."
              }
            }
